=Description=

"Our mission is to create a global technology platform that empowers local community resilience and generates real prosperity. By bringing people together around what matters most, transforming latent resources into higher quality living, and fostering an ecosystem of caring in community, we will build
cleaner communities, happier people, and a world we can be proud to pass to the next generation.

From peer-to-peer Time-banking, to business-to-business commercial credit clearing, there is a full spectrum of ways communities can use resources effectively, creatively, and sustainably. We provide guidance and technology to support your community and its goals for a healthier, wealthier future."


